cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper is about natural language understanding (NLU) using neural networks and the integration of background knowledge. The most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it specifically deals with NLU. The paper also involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) techniques. Information retrieval (cs.IR) is also relevant as the paper deals with document question answering. Finally, neural networks (cs.NE) are used in the proposed architecture.
